Message.SourceString: You've crafted some runes I see, good. Magic is a tool, just like any other, but one worth keeping around.
Message.LocalizedString: You've crafted some runes I see, good. Magic is a tool, just like any other, but one worth keeping around.

Message.SourceString: Not made any runes yet? It's quite simple really, you just need to find a source of rune essence.
Message.LocalizedString: Not made any runes yet? It's quite simple really, you just need to find a source of rune essence.

Message.SourceString: There's a deposit of essence behind this temple. Go mine it, then build yourself a rune altar. You might want to get yourself a pickaxe.
Message.LocalizedString: There's a deposit of essence behind this temple. Go mine it, then build yourself a rune altar. You might want to get yourself a pickaxe.

Message.SourceString: When you've done that, craft yourself some air runes at the altar.
Message.LocalizedString: When you've done that, craft yourself some air runes at the altar.

Message.SourceString: You'll discover several spells as you improve your skills. Try experimenting with all of them. Magic is fun!
Message.LocalizedString: You'll discover several spells as you improve your skills. Try experimenting with all of them. Magic is fun!

Message.SourceString: Now, onto the scary stuff. You'll want to talk to Vannaka next. He'll help you avoid a brutal and agonising death...maybe. Have fun!
Message.LocalizedString: Now, onto the scary stuff. You'll want to talk to Vannaka next. He'll help you avoid a brutal and agonising death...maybe. Have fun!

Message.SourceString: Runes are made from rune essence, a special kind of stone that absorbs and holds magical power - anima.
Message.LocalizedString: Runes are made from rune essence, a special kind of stone that absorbs and holds magical power - anima.

Message.SourceString: There's a deposit of essence behind this temple. Go mine it, then build yourself a rune altar. You might want to get yourself a pickaxe.
Message.LocalizedString: There's a deposit of essence behind this temple. Go mine it, then build yourself a rune altar. You might want to get yourself a pickaxe.

Message.SourceString: When you've done that, craft yourself some air runes at the altar.
Message.LocalizedString: When you've done that, craft yourself some air runes at the altar.

Message.SourceString: Runes, right? Thousands of years ago Guthix created special stones containing magical power. Runes.
Message.LocalizedString: Runes, right? Thousands of years ago Guthix created special stones containing magical power. Runes.

Message.SourceString: Aren't you helping the others out? What are you talking to me for? Check your map if you're not sure what you're meant to be doing.
